Cressida Bonas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cressida_Bonas 0 Cressida Curzon Bonas (born 18 February 1989) is an English actress and model. She is the youngest daughter of Lady Mary-Gaye Curzon and entrepreneur Jeffrey Bonas, and a granddaughter of Edward Curzon, 6th Earl Howe.
